1\u885709.jpg|[[Yu Jen Jai]] (1930)\nFile:Hayashi Department Store (night).jpg|[[Hayashi Department Store]], Tainan (1922)\nFile:\u53f0\u4e2d\u5dde\u5ef3\uff08\u820a\u53f0\u4e2d\u5e02\u653f\u5e9c\uff09.jpg|[[Taichung City Hall]], Taichung (1924)\nFile:Taipei Post Office front view 20181018.jpg|[[Taipei Post Office]], Taipei (1928)\nFile:Kaohsiung Museum of History face 20101031.jpg|Kaohsiung Museum of History, Kaohsiung (1939)\nFile:Taipei Taiwan Judicial-Yuan-01.jpg|[[Taiwan High Court]], Taipei (1934)\nFile:Sansia IMG 1625.JPG|[[Sanxia Old Street]], (1916)\nFile:Taipei Taiwan Zhongshan-Hall-01.jpg|[[Zhongshan Hall|Public Hall]], Taipei (1936)\nFile:Taipei Taiwan Bank-of-Taiwan-Head-Office-Building-01.jpg|[[Bank of Taiwan]] (1938)\nFile:Taichung Broadcasting Bureau.JPG|[[Taichung Broadcasting Bureau]], Taichung\n</gallery>\n\n;[[Chinese architecture]]\n<gallery>\nFile:\u6de1\u6c34\u6232\u9928.jpg|New State (Tamsui Theater), [[Twatutia]], Taipei.\n</gallery>\n\n;[[Japanese architecture]]\n<gallery>\nFile:\u5609\u7fa9\u795e\u793e\u9644\u5c6c\u9928\u6240.jpg|[[Kagi Shrine]] administration building, Kagi, [[Tainan Prefecture]] (Chiayi, 1915)\nFile:Taoyuan Martyrs&#039; Shrine 09.jpg|[[Touen Shrine]] [[Haiden (Shinto)|Haiden]] (1938)\nFile:\u6b66\u5fb7\u6bbf hall of military morality - panoramio.jpg|[[Kaohsiung Wude Hall|Takao Butokuden]], [[Takao Prefecture]] (Kaohsiung, 1924)\nFile:\u53f0\u5317\u7d00\u5dde\u5eb5.jpg|Kishu An Forest of Literature in Taipei\nFile:Tainan Taiwan Martial-Art-Hall Butokuden-01.jpg|[[Tainan Butokuden]], [[Tainan Prefecture]] (Tainan 1936)\nFile:Budokan by Taichung Takenori Hall.JPG|Taichu Prison Dojo, [[Taichu Prefecture]] (Taichung)\nFile:\u5317\u6295\u6587\u7269\u9928(\u539f\u4f73\u5c71\u65c5\u9928).jpg|[[Beitou Museum]], Taipei (1921)\nFile:\u4e00\u6ef4\u6c34\u7d00\u5ff5\u9928 A Drop of Water Memorial Hall - panoramio.jpg|The [[Drop of Water Memorial Hall]], Taipei (1915)\nFile:\u81fa\u7063\u7e3d\u7763\u5e9c\u5c08\u8ce3\u5c40\u81fa\u5357\